  "title": "chore(deps): update dependency style-loader to v0.19.0",
  "body": "<p>This Pull Request updates dependency <a href=\"https://github.com/webpack/style-loader\">style-loader</a> from <code>v0.18.2</code> to <code>v0.19.0</code></p>\n<h3 id=\"commits\">Commits</h3>\n<p><details><br />\n<summary>webpack/style-loader</summary></p>\n<h4 id=\"0190\">0.19.0</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/webpack/style-loader/commit/c9707f12ff46f8e142607e0c43a0939cc76e48f8\"><code>c9707f1</code></a> chore(release): 0.19.0</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/webpack/style-loader/commit/378e90637f1c2c30bff026d7f92bdc82d9d4ecb8\"><code>378e906</code></a> feat: add option to enable/disable HMR (<code>options.hmr</code>) (#&#8203;264)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/webpack/style-loader/commit/67120f8dc831626f466d64513b4e26074e89341b\"><code>67120f8</code></a> feat: support &#x27;before&#x27; insertions (<code>options.insertAt</code>) (#&#8203;253)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/webpack/style-loader/commit/a2ae3ac65e8e802d1d96b5ee5170c8ecefeeec74\"><code>a2ae3ac</code></a> docs(README): fix bash code highlight (#&#8203;262)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/webpack/style-loader/commit/ce53bd92b392e10940c7cc4ad56a780b47e7b1f0\"><code>ce53bd9</code></a> docs(readme): fix typo (#&#8203;260)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/webpack/style-loader/commit/57e171fe74a5f39aeb90dbcc5a1d1c2cf1a94334\"><code>57e171f</code></a> docs: Fixes typo in readme (#&#8203;258)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/webpack/style-loader/commit/01ceef8ded6b94c4fff95e832a11354e8fd4413f\"><code>01ceef8</code></a> docs(README): fix example (<code>options.insertInto</code>) (#&#8203;251)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/webpack/style-loader/commit/25e8e89b1f9c434162627ca3c2750d1796f58c1d\"><code>25e8e89</code></a> feat: add support for iframes (<code>options.insertInto</code>) (#&#8203;248)</li>\n</ul>\n<p></details></p>\n<hr />\n<p>This PR has been generated by <a href=\"https://renovateapp.com\">Renovate Bot</a>.</p>",
